---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import Sidenote from '../../components/Sidenote.astro';
---

<Base title="Content Leverage">
  <article>
    <h1>Content Leverage</h1>
    <p class="subtitle" style="font-size: 1.2rem; font-style: italic; color: var(--color-text-muted);">
      One input, seven outputs. Never create for one platform only.
    </p>

    <h2>The Leverage Stack</h2>

    <pre><code>1 Lab Session (90 min)
    ├── Recording → YouTube (full)
    ├── Key demo → YouTube Short / Reel (60s)
    ├── 3 insights → 3 LinkedIn posts
    ├── Transcript → Blog post
    ├── Q&A highlights → FAQ page
    ├── Participant quote → Testimonial
    └── Skill used → Skill demo video</code></pre>

    <p>
      Ratio: 1 input → 7+ outputs.
      <Sidenote id="ratio">
        Agents handle the decomposition: transcript extraction, platform-specific formatting,
        translation (RU → EN, EN → DE), metadata generation. Human role: review, approve,
        add personal voice.
      </Sidenote>
    </p>

    <h2>Minimum Viable Content Calendar</h2>

    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr><th>Day</th><th>Action</th><th>Time</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Mon</td><td>Review agent suggestions</td><td>10 min</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Tue</td><td>Lab session (natural content)</td><td>90 min</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Wed</td><td>Post 1 LinkedIn insight</td><td>5 min</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Thu</td><td>Record 1 skill demo</td><td>15 min</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Fri</td><td>Share demo + engage</td><td>10 min</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Sat</td><td>Lab practice (natural content)</td><td>60 min</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Sun</td><td>Review agent weekly report</td><td>5 min</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <p><strong>Total active content work: ~3.5 hours/week</strong></p>
  </article>
</Base>
